dct_description_sm: published by Samuel Walker ; G. Boynton sc.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
2 bar scales on map given in "Turkish miles" and "British statute miles".
Shows topography, drainage, land and sea travel routes, places of historical interest.
Appears in Walker's Walker atlas of world.
